  "description": "Impact assessment on the extension of the right to request flexible working to all employees.",
  "details": {
    "body": "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Since the original publication of this assessment in November 2012, the Better Regulation Executive has updated the inflation assumptions that are used to discount the costs and benefits of all policies. As a result, the equivalent annual net cost to business of the policies assessed has fallen to £10.31 million (down from £11.79 million). The remaining analysis is unchanged.</p>\n\n<p>This document relates to the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/consultations/consultation-on-modern-workplaces\">consultation on modern workplaces</a>.</p>\n</div>",
